{Speech 2}{}{Damn piece o' brahmin shit!@@Fucking one-handed raider! Pay Old McGee!@@Enough cheating with Old McGee, darling...@@Everything is against me again!@@One more time...@@I will get my fukcin' cash back, even if I have to spend here all year round...@@Die die die, my darling slots!@@Maybe it's my lucky day!@@I will win today. Lady Fortune'll make sure it will be a nine.@@[Punches the slots machine]@@Shit, I got no money left! Again!@@Everything is against me again!@@I need to find some more coins!@@Damn slot! It swallows up all my cash!}
